    <entry>
      <title>用hexo和git搭建个人博客</title>
      <link href="/2018/10/25/%E7%94%A8hexo%E5%92%8Cgit%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
      <url>/2018/10/25/%E7%94%A8hexo%E5%92%8Cgit%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="用hexo-github-搭建个人博客"><a href="#用hexo-github-搭建个人博客" class="headerlink" title="用hexo+github 搭建个人博客"></a>用hexo+github 搭建个人博客</h1><p><a href="http://htmler.cn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">样板参考</a> </p><h2 id="一·环境搭建"><a href="#一·环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="一·环境搭建"></a>一·环境搭建</h2><p>1·node<br> why? hexo是一款基于node开发出来的博客框架<br> what?node:基于JavaScript语法的一款WEB服务器<br> how?  <a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官网地址</a>选择V8.X版本<br>2·git (版本控制器) 分布式<br>what 版本控制器<br>github 全球最大的开源代码托管平台<br>why 通过github托管博客项目<br>how <a href="https://git-scm.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官网</a> 下载安装包</p><h2 id="二-项目环境搭建"><a href="#二-项目环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="二.项目环境搭建"></a>二.项目环境搭建</h2><p>1·安装hexo脚手架：通过npm包管理器<br>npm:基于Node的包管理器(类似于APP store)<br>原生 ==》 插件==》 框架</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-cli -g <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#安装hexo依赖包</span><span class="token function">install</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#导入 安装</span>hexo-cli:hexo <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#脚手架  </span><span class="token function">clear</span> ctrl+L <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#清屏</span>-g <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#全局安装 global  （对应局部）</span></code></pre><p>2·npm切换淘宝镜像 解决npm国内慢的问题</p><h2 id="三-初始化一个博客项目"><a href="#三-初始化一个博客项目" class="headerlink" title="三.初始化一个博客项目"></a>三.初始化一个博客项目</h2><p>1.在桌面右键“git bash here”<br>2.初始化项目</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo init blog <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#初始化文件夹</span></code></pre><p>3.切换blog文件夹</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">cd</span> blog    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#change dirte</span><span class="token function">ls</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#显示当前路径文件   </span><span class="token function">ls</span> -a <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#显示当前路径所有文件</span><span class="token function">pwd</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#显示当前全路径    </span></code></pre><p>4.安装项目依赖包</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#安装命令</span></code></pre><p>5.启动hexo服务</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo s           <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#启动服务server </span>ctrl+c  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 关闭服务</span></code></pre><p><a href="http://localhost:4000" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:4000</a>   关闭是 </p><h2 id="四-Linux常用命令"><a href="#四-Linux常用命令" class="headerlink" title="四.Linux常用命令"></a>四.Linux常用命令</h2><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">cd</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#目录名   路径切换</span><span class="token function">pwd</span>         <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#查看当前路径</span><span class="token function">ls</span> -a       <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#查看当前路径所有文件及目录</span><span class="token function">cd</span> <span class="token punctuation">..</span>      <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#回到上级目录</span></code></pre><p>下载 VSCODE 安装<br>选择打开文件夹bolg<br>source 源文件 _posts 页面文章内容<br>nod_modules 全部安装包<br>.gitignore  不需要上传的文件<br>{}package.json   </p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">ctrl+~ <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#呼出服务器控制</span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
